title: Walter Taibo
text: Wálter Taibo Martínez (7 March 1931 – 10 January 2021) was a <a href="Uruguay">Uruguay</a>an <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a> who played for <a href="Uruguay%20national%20football%20team">Uruguay</a> in the <a href="1966%20FIFA%20World%20Cup">1966 FIFA World Cup</a>. He also played for <a href="C.A.%20Pe%C3%B1arol">C.A. Peñarol</a>. In Argentina, he played for <a href="Club%20Atl%C3%A9tico%20Hurac%C3%A1n">Huracán</a> in 1959-60.
